The paper discusses using reinforcement learning to train robots in various tasks, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of self-models and transfer learning also involves machine learning techniques such as deep learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of predictive models to achieve tasks, which can be related to control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the use of simulated robots and the mention of visual inputs suggests that computer vision (cs.CV) may also be relevant.
